RICE definition (by https://github.com/neeasade/):

A potential backronym for rice is Race Inspired Cosmetic Enhancements,
supposedly a term taken from the car mod community to refer to changes/mods
that were done mostly for aesthetic reasons (i.e., performance was not
affected or went down).
